@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ddwijx(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = ((v1 - (tmp + 0.72 / v0 + 0.89)) + 0.84)
    tmp = ((tmp - (v1 + 0.28 - tmp + 0.02)) - ((v1 + 0.35 - v2 + 0.57) + (v0 + 0.39 - v2 + 0.28)))
    tmp = wp.exp(0.07)
    v0 = wp.sin(0.14)
    v0 = (0.14 + wp.abs((v0 + 0.14 + v1 + 0.74)))
    tmp = 0.34
    v0 = wp.abs(v0)
    data[tid] = v0
